  "detailed_description": "<h1>More Game</h1><p><br><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>This is a contaminated world!<br>As a fighting girl, you have the ability to clear these monsters.<br>What troubles do you get into when cleaning up monsters?<br>Welcome to experience it!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092260/extras/2f8a21bb1115ebd7bfe9cee8d599ebb6.poster.avif?t=1708494508\" width=480 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092260/extras/2f8a21bb1115ebd7bfe9cee8d599ebb6.webm?t=1708494508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092260/extras/2f8a21bb1115ebd7bfe9cee8d599ebb6.mp4?t=1708494508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Extremely Striking feeling<br></li><li>Up to four combo attacks<br></li><li>Challenge difficulty can be switched at any time<br></li><li>Great background music<br></li><li>There are five levels to challenge</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092260/extras/8aa5418c944203d9fde48819bf915c09.poster.avif?t=1708494508\" width=480 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092260/extras/8aa5418c944203d9fde48819bf915c09.webm?t=1708494508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092260/extras/8aa5418c944203d9fde48819bf915c09.mp4?t=1708494508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092260/extras/c3691a7bc0fee3a08ec00e